{"tid":145083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶扮live] 送禮佳品 挖空本書做賀卡","createTime":"2017-03-06T03:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T01:26:00.000Z","uid":1022,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2698ec0be26a543b42bfe9b2c3556f9f7114f7d8","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"Hi又係我<br />\n扮工時間無野做黎回個帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年聖誕節整左本簿，中間挖左個窿放d野入去做聖誕卡送比男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得自己好撚勁，share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q80SiJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq80SiJW.jpg&h=b37c0974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先梗係要買本簿啦，最緊要夠厚<br />\n唔好咁大本，如果唔係𠝹撚到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢本野我係cotton on買既，好似係schedule book黎<br />\n但我無影到個樣係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8be338a2fc179e71deac43c2b872e79e0f38dce","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/113226_16ac86f88b902b9e0c06668e0d444a78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F113226_16ac86f88b902b9e0c06668e0d444a78.jpg&h=295b4171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係用果d筆刀𠝹既，每次𠝹到3,4層<br />\n其實用𠝹刀有效率d，不過我太粗魯廢事𠝹爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者，我每日返工𠝹下，返屋企𠝹下<br />\n𠝹左個幾星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e01e91d3b0a64e256d9f075f5a0bf2b4362a3a1","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷留下正皮走左去!!<br />\n<br />\n睇緊都出句聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2316d56be70b9c8cf0895db018b7884f04614249","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3G76H0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3G76H0.jpg&h=6bf479c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n挖到差唔多既時候<br />\n印左句我中意既quote係塊膠片度做個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(要用laser printer先印到好似係)"},{"pid":"4c1373de62674e4ac91ecea04a9eafc67d0ad9c6","tid":145083,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"界到手軟"},{"pid":"7380bb8279075b1d38a52def35fe56ecdc3c1456","tid":145083,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"磨返平D界位先吧"},{"pid":"539daf4d210e5455bc4b96a02caa292257167849","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>界到手軟</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n整到一半想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d1941aba861ae91d96554d1187d54ce35133b6","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/114954_4750cd0ea57a7d70b2521077e61ad656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F114954_4750cd0ea57a7d70b2521077e61ad656.jpg&h=559a14b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係模型舖買左隻人仔<br />\n原本想買結婚公仔，但好似催婚咁<br />\n所以算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n丁屎咁大隻都60幾蚊，事後係淘寶見到幾蚊都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ybt92MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbt92MA.jpg&h=60cb5424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後又買左樽假雪<br />\n其實心目中想買粉狀沈落去，不過佢得呢隻就是但<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e14e11ee3fd78b1abf34e1e771532d8d96d8fc","tid":145083,"uid":79469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:57:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"83eee6374b672e6a00ad71ddf36c8af8ee669fe4","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"點解做手工都要負皮我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6af5219fa20b43c6eeb3bcb62699f346b03bf5","tid":145083,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"幫你比返個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce0f8abfe2dbca7e429fa499e797c1f2b6ea1e2","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你比返個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d754c028d70e2b8f705a70c9b22ca1f5ba2d71d1","tid":145083,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f158ab3ab943280d706673701164816d1244c57a","tid":145083,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tespsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tespsC.jpg&h=cb617612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個過程無影低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係膠片印左棵樹，諗住倒d凸粉落去效果靚d<br />\nOn9點知熱風槍吹到塊膠彎鳩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉是但啦照痴落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後痴埋隻人仔，用水彩筆印d雪落去"},{"pid":"5724ae726ee1df30e6e42ce867b8f78ce2391375","tid":145083,"uid":41131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,